This is a really poorly made drawing program via ncurses it's sort of like a sketch. I started from somebody elses code 
that I modified with the help of the ncurses tutorial. The original source was example 9 from here: 

	http://invisible-island.net/ncurses/NCURSES-Programming-HOWTO.html#KEYS

The unused midinote class is a scratch as I plan to try and make midifiles with this at somepoint.. For now you can just draw with it! :]
